org.gvsig.remoteClient.arcims
Class ArcImsStatus

java.lang.Object
  org.gvsig.remoteClient.RemoteClientStatus
      org.gvsig.remoteClient.arcims.ArcImsStatus
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ArcImsVectStatus
public class ArcImsStatus
extends RemoteClientStatus
implements java.lang.Cloneable

Describes the status of a ArcImsclient, so it adds to the Remote client status a list of layers, a list of layer styles, the extent of the map. Provides the functionality to modify these lists.

Author:
jcarrasco, jsanz
See Also:
RemoteClientStatus
